<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="3" type="materials_examined">
<paragraph blockId="2.[869,1494,730,915]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[869,994,730,755]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">
<typeStatus box="[869,926,730,755]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Type</typeStatus>
data:
</emphasis>
This species was described based on an undetermined number of specimens of both sexes collect‑ ed in the province of 
<collectingRegion box="[1107,1210,794,819]" country="Argentina" name="San Juan" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">San Juan</collectingRegion>
, northwestern 
<collectingCountry box="[1377,1490,794,819]" name="Argentina" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Argentina</collectingCountry>
. The 
<typeStatus box="[919,969,826,851]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">type</typeStatus>
series was not found during the development of this research and it is apparently lost (
<bibRefCitation author="Roig-Alsina, A." pageId="2" pageNumber="3" pagination="171 - 193" refId="ref4820" refString="Roig-Alsina, A. 2000. Claves para las especies argentinas de Centris (Hymenoptera, Apidae), con descripcion de nuevas especies y notas sobre distribucion. Revista del Museo Argentino de Ciencias Naturales, 2 (2): 171 - 193." type="journal article" year="2000">Roig‑Alsina, 2000</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="3" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="2.[869,1494,954,1299]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[869,1004,954,979]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Comments:</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Schrottky, C." box="[1017,1220,954,979]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" pagination="309 - 315" refId="ref4866" refString="Schrottky, C. 1902 a. Hymenopteres noveaux de l'Amerique Meridionale. Anales del Museo Nacional de Buenos Aires, 7: 309 - 315." type="journal article" year="1902">Schrottky (1902a)</bibRefCitation>
dedicated this species to the Argentinean zoologist and ornithologist Enrique Lynch Arribálzaga (1856‑1935) who funded with his countryman the botanist, zoologist and geologist Eduardo Ladislao Holmberg (1852‑1937) in 1878 “El Naturalista Argentino”, the first journal of Natural History of 
<collectingCountry box="[899,1009,1146,1171]" name="Argentina" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Argentina</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Lopez, H. L. &amp; Miquelarena, A. M. &amp; Gomez, J. P." box="[1023,1223,1146,1171]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" pagination="1 - 73" refId="ref4255" refString="Lopez, H. L.; Miquelarena, A. M. &amp; Gomez, J. P. 2008. Ictiologos de la Argentina Eduardo Ladislao Holmberg. ProBiota, FCN y M. UNLP Serie Tecnica y Didactica, 14 (1): 1 - 73." type="journal article" year="2008">
López 
<emphasis box="[1101,1159,1146,1171]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">et al.,</emphasis>
2008
</bibRefCitation>
). This species occurs exclusively in 
<collectingCountry box="[1007,1117,1178,1203]" name="Argentina" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Argentina</collectingCountry>
with distribution records in the provinces of 
<collectingRegion box="[1019,1168,1210,1235]" country="Argentina" name="Ciudad Autonoma de Buenos Aires" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Buenos Aires</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingRegion box="[1180,1301,1210,1235]" country="Argentina" name="Catamarca" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Catamarca</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingRegion box="[1314,1386,1210,1235]" country="Argentina" name="Chaco" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Chaco</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingRegion box="[1398,1491,1210,1235]" country="Argentina" name="La Rioja" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">La Rioja</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingRegion box="[869,975,1242,1267]" country="Argentina" name="Mendoza" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Mendoza</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingRegion box="[987,1082,1242,1267]" country="Argentina" name="San Luis" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">San Luis</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingRegion box="[1093,1191,1242,1267]" country="Argentina" name="Santa Fe" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Santa Fe</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingRegion box="[1202,1423,1242,1267]" country="Argentina" name="Santiago del Estero" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Santiago del Estero</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingRegion box="[1433,1490,1242,1267]" country="Argentina" name="Salta" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Salta</collectingRegion>
, and 
<collectingRegion box="[917,1020,1274,1299]" country="Argentina" name="Tucuman" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Tucumán</collectingRegion>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Roig-Alsina, A." box="[1031,1229,1274,1299]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" pagination="171 - 193" refId="ref4820" refString="Roig-Alsina, A. 2000. Claves para las especies argentinas de Centris (Hymenoptera, Apidae), con descripcion de nuevas especies y notas sobre distribucion. Revista del Museo Argentino de Ciencias Naturales, 2 (2): 171 - 193." type="journal article" year="2000">Roig‑Alsina, 2000</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
